<font color="#FF0000">VIETNAM</font><br>
<tt>Sat Jan 17 16:00:23 US/Eastern 1998
</tt><p>
Vietnam anchored a generation of people, especially early baby boomers to take the world seriously, it may be your life so it is important to look at it. Self interest in this country is so strong that to look beyond what helps the individual is tough, thus a generation X, self satisfied and self interested. It is difficult to inspire people to do good in the world when they have not had a kick such as Vietnam was to another potentially self centered group, the post war boomers.<br>

